   |                    | users can update using the system update feature  |
   |                    |          in the appliance control panel.          |
   |--------------------+---------------------------------------------------|
   | Asterisk Appliance |               0.5.0, available from               |
   |   Developer Kit    |                                                   |
   |                    |     ftp://ftp.digium.com/pub/telephony/aadk/      |
